Anomaly Detection System
Overview
This Anomaly Detection System is designed to identify unusual patterns in data using machine learning techniques. It can be applied to fraud detection, network security, predictive maintenance, and other domains where detecting irregularities is crucial.
Features
●Supervised and unsupervised anomaly detection models
●Real-time and batch processing support
●Scalable architecture for large datasets
●Visualization of anomalies for better insights
●API integration for seamless deployment
Installation
Clone the repository:
 git clone https://github.com/your-repo.git  
cd your-repo  
1.
Install dependencies:
 pip install -r requirements.txt  
2.
Run the system:
 python main.py  
3.
Usage
Modify configurations in config.yaml to tune detection parameters. Use the API for integrating with existing applications.
